name: TezOwl #13: Plasma
description:
TezOwls are a unique NFT species of owls. When they hatch from their eggs they change the structure of their bodies to quickly adapt to the environment, for this reason a lot of different and unique TezOwls can be discovered.

TezOwls is a collection of procedurally and AI generated owls. 

Mirai.art (@Mir_AI_Art)
